# Demo: Update Check
# Shows /update command

Output docs/images/demo-update.gif

Set Shell "pwsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai --new --force-update-check"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "/update"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Screenshot docs/images/demo-update.png
Sleep 2s
